{"tid":303372,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[過黎一齊玩啦喂]連登大運動會報名處","createTime":"2017-06-30T06:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T07:30:20.000Z","uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7123a1b29062c7d512b9fbc606c1057fce5382","tid":303372,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">．參賽者需年滿18歲或以上<br />\n．不限男女，但必需持有真實的陰莖<br />\n．大會建議各參賽者參賽前購買保險<br />\n<br />\n丁丁舉啞鈴<br />\n<br />\n各位參賽者需要將連接啞鈴的繩索綁在<strong>未勃起</strong>的陰莖上，然後在三分鐘內勃起，將啞鈴提升至離開地面20cm或以上保持10秒作為紀錄。<br />\n每位參賽者均有三次試舉機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n丁丁神槍<br />\n<br />\n各位參賽者需要將小便成功命中貼在尿兜上一張港女照片的口中，過程不能以肢體或道具接觸陰莖，每位參賽者有三次試射機會，其中一次距離最遠參賽者為優勝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n丁丁破木板<br />\n<br />\n參賽者需要用自己的陰莖打破每塊厚度2CM的木板，參賽者可要求木板數量，每位參賽者只有一次機會，打破木板數最多的參賽者為優勝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n丁丁瑞典接力 （Swedish relay）<br />\n<br />\n參賽者需要組隊，四人為一組，第一名跑者需要「賽跑」100米，第二名200米，第三名300名，第四名400米。每位參賽者需要一邊令大會提供的一名同性戀男士勃起並一邊前進。參賽者不能踩踏於賽道之外，時間最快的組別為之優勝。</div>"},{"pid":"09c27afc5fb49bebace5f2ee27791d7ca9148a7a","tid":303372,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"因為第一次搞比賽，搞次幾項簡單先架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d4e6709cdd103d065627ed8a422135cdaf358b","tid":303372,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6dc81033dc15100a4e7dda1da9b60b79315aa4","tid":303372,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad03a7d4453abbb75d6f417e6a229eeae18bab0a","tid":303372,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13d0fc085625a290467db0bcf22aba488d4faa4","tid":303372,"uid":6242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"樓主你到底知唔知2cm木板係有幾撚厚?<br />\n打完篇野出來有冇起雞皮?"},{"pid":"2ea1ee2d702913fa95321dc53946f156414d0ca8","tid":303372,"uid":68073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你到底知唔知2cm木板係有幾撚厚?<br />\n打完篇野出來有冇起雞皮?</blockquote><br />\n廢"},{"pid":"98c9400ce270ece4c5f2d3e623bb96505e97fe0d","tid":303372,"uid":6242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:16:07.000Z","msg":"樓主幾多歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42197ddd7568f6f982c3c2c217780856bae6283","tid":303372,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:20:19.000Z","msg":"樓主打完篇文之後有冇成功感？"},{"pid":"020668e3eae9c859b18b3e6863983abfd3c1f987","tid":303372,"uid":66119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"樓主打完之後有冇睇下紅館比唔比個期到你開show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}